title: Simple Stitches Knits with Textured Details
description: Welcome to stress-free knitting! Here you'll find classic, stylish patterns that are simple and fun to knit. Garter, stockinette, seed stitch, and other old-favourites come to life in timeless designs with clever detailing. Uncomplicated lines and minimal finishing will keep you coming back to these 16 projects time and again. Discover your creative side with these simple and stylish knitted designs with elegant detail.
